item.title: HAB you seen our balloons?
item.author: Zoe Versey,
item.description: On Sunday 5 May, members of Imperial College Students for the Exploration and Development of Space (ICSEDS) travelled to Elsworth, Cambridgeshire for their first launch. The aim was to launch two high altitude balloons (HABs) and several model rockets built over the course of the year. The two HABs â€¦
